-bextor">Sophie Ellis-Bextor</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/becky-hill">Becky Hill</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/busted">Busted</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/craig-david">Craig David</a> 、DJ Spoony 以及嘉宾、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Rudimental">Rudimental</a> l 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paloma-faith">帕洛玛·费思</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-savoretti">杰克·萨沃雷蒂</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jls">JLS</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jess-glynne">杰西·格林</a>。</p><p></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/devo-madness-descendents-billy-bragg-and-more-for-punk-rock-bowling-2024-line-up-3558474">《朋克摇滚保龄球 2024》阵容的后 Devo、Madness、Descendents、Billy Bragg 等首发阵容</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
